00:00:52.920 --> 00:00:55.723 align:middle line:84%
and the stress and
there is this place

00:00:55.723 --> 00:00:56.924 align:middle line:90%
where we can find ourselves

00:00:56.924 --> 00:00:59.994 align:middle line:84%
where there's just you
