actually makes those nerves get

00:30:44.009 --> 00:30:45.077 align:middle line:90%
closer together.

00:30:45.077 --> 00:30:47.313 align:middle line:84%
So there's less of a
gap for them to jump

00:30:47.313 --> 00:30:50.316 align:middle line:84%
and the pathways you don't use,
so the pathways of calm start

00:30:50.316 --> 00:30:51.817 align:middle line:90%
to become farther apart.

00:30:51.817 --> 00:30:55.921 align:middle line:84%
So if you're using a pathway a
lot it becomes stronger and one

00:30:55.921 --> 00:30:57.122 align:middle line:84%
