00:38:03.014 --> 00:38:05.050 align:middle line:84%
Those are the times
when we most notice it

00:38:05.050 --> 00:38:08.153 align:middle line:90%
but what would it be like.

00:38:08.153 --> 00:38:09.755 align:middle line:84%
Like that question you
were asking, what more?

00:38:09.755 --> 00:38:12.057 align:middle line:84%
What would it be like
if we could actually be

00:38:12.057 --> 00:38:15.761 align:middle line:84%
in the present, in the
moment, in this moment, now,

00:38:15.761 --> 00:38:18.463 align:middle line:90%
here ongoingly, what then?

00:38:18.463 --> 00:38:20.165 align:middle line:84%
Because a lot of the
stress for instance,

00:38:20.165 --> 00:38:23.068 align:middle line:84%
stress is not a present
moment then phenomenon.

00:38:23.068 --> 00:38:25.504 align:middle line:84%
It's all about what
will happen next?

00:38:25.504 --> 00:38:28.206 align:middle line:84%
Anxiety is all about
the future tense.

00:38:28.206 --> 00:38:29.174 align:middle line:84%
We're note stressed
about the past.

00:38:29.174 --> 00:38:30.675 align:middle line:84%
We can't be stressed
about the past.

00:38:30.675 --> 00:38:32.978 align:middle line:84%
We can be regretful,
remorseful and guilty.

00:38:32.978 --> 00:38:34.980 align:middle line:84%
We can't be stressed
about the past.

00:38:34.980 --> 00:38:36.715 align:middle line:84%
We can do stressed
about the consequences

00:38:36.715 --> 00:38:38.383 align:middle line:90%
into the future of that past.

00:38:38.383 --> 00:38:40.986 align:middle line:84%
So being in the present
actually allow us

00:38:40.986 --> 00:38:44.790 align:middle line:84%
to suddenly just put aside those
conversations about the past

00:38:44.790 --> 00:38:46.158 align:middle line:90%
which are mainly irrelevant

00:38:46.158 --> 00:38:48.293 align:middle line:84%
because the past doesn't even
exist anymore and the future

00:38:48.293 --> 00:38:50.162 align:middle line:90%
which is yet designed by us.

00:38:50.162 --> 00:38:51.997 align:middle line:84%
So yeah, being present
is actually essential.

00:38:51.997 --> 00:38:55.267 align:middle line:84%
>> Lilou: Because we can't
really control other people

00:38:55.267 --> 00:38:56.368 align:middle line:90%
