00:39:05.477 --> 00:39:07.879 align:middle line:84%
to change the weather,
it's just ridiculous.

00:39:07.879 --> 00:39:08.647 align:middle line:90%
We've all tried it.

00:39:08.647 --> 00:39:09.347 align:middle line:90%
It doesn't work.

00:39:09.347 --> 00:39:10.715 align:middle line:90%
We should get over it.

00:39:10.715 --> 00:39:14.319 align:middle line:84%
Find a way to deal with
ourselves not try and find a way

00:39:14.319 --> 00:39:15.887 align:middle line:90%
